<p>NIST SP 800-31, Intrusion Detection Systems <a href="http://csrc.nist.gov/publications/nistpubs/index.html" class="external free" title="http://csrc.nist.gov/publications/nistpubs/index.html" rel="nofollow">http://csrc.nist.gov/publications/nistpubs/index.html</a></p>
<p>Study by Gartner "Host-Based Intrusion Prevention Systems (HIPS) Update: Why Antivirus and Personal Firewall Technologies Aren't Enough" <a href="http://www.gartner.com/teleconferences/attributes/attr_165281_115.pdf" class="external free" title="http://www.gartner.com/teleconferences/attributes/attr_165281_115.pdf" rel="nofollow">http://www.gartner.com/teleconferences/attributes/attr_165281_115.pdf</a></p>
<p>Study by Gartner "Magic Quadrant for Network Intrusion Prevention System Appliances, 1H08" <a href="http://www-935.ibm.com/services/us/iss/pdf/esr_magic-quadrant-for-network-intrusion-prevention-system-appliances-1h08.pdf" class="external free" title="http://www-935.ibm.com/services/us/iss/pdf/esr_magic-quadrant-for-network-intrusion-prevention-system-appliances-1h08.pdf" rel="nofollow">http://www-935.ibm.com/services/us/iss/pdf/esr_magic-quadrant-for-network-intrusion-prevention-system-appliances-1h08.pdf</a></p>
