<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Intrusion-prevention_system&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11" title="Edit section: Open Source Intrusion Prevention Systems">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Open Source Intrusion Prevention Systems</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Lokkit&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Lokkit (page does not exist)">Lokkit</a> (GNOME)</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Snort_(software)" title="Snort (software)">Snort</a>: The de facto standard for IDS/IPS used by network security professionals today.</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Untangle" title="Untangle">Untangle</a>: Excellent Linux gateway distribution suitable for Small-to-Medium size business.</li>
</ul>
